<i>adjective</i>: 적법하다 [적뻐파다] <i>determiner</i>: 합법적 [합뻡쩍], 법적 [법쩍], 법률적 [범뉼쩍] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>적법하다 [적뻐파다]</dt><br>
<dd>legal</dd><br>
<dd>정해진 법규에 맞다.</dd><br>
<dd>Complying with a specific law.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>determiner</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>합법적 [합뻡쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>legal; legitimate; lawful</dd><br>
<dd>법과 규범에 맞는.</dd><br>
<dd>In accordance with law and rule.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>법적 [법쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>legal; legalistic</dd><br>
<dd>법에 따른.</dd><br>
<dd>Being based on the law.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>법률적 [범뉼쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>legal</dd><br>
<dd>법과 관계되는.</dd><br>
<dd>Being related to the law.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>